  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You are skilled at fighting with two weapons.</em> <br /><br /></p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong></p>\n<p>Dex 17, Two-Weapon Fighting, base attack bonus +6.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p class=\"stat-block-1\">In addition to the standard single extra attack you get with an off-hand weapon, you get a second attack with it, albeit at a &ndash;5 penalty.</p>\n<p class=\"stat-block-1\">Once your BAB reaches +11, you also gain a third attack with your off-hand weapon, albeit at a -10 penalty.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Normal</strong></p>\n<p class=\"stat-block-1\">Without this feat, you can only get a single extra attack with an off-hand weapon.</p>",
